	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I guess it's pretty simple how it does it. It turns the screen blanked for a frame, and mask a bit in all tiles of the BG pattern table used for the background.
<br />
<br />I've also asked myself about the scaling IV. It's really a mystery.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


