	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I considered using the emphasis bits, like I mentioned before, but gave up on the idea for a number of reasons.
<br />
<br />I ended up solving my problem by reordering the palette so that it's more friendly to hue and brightness transformations. The conversion table ended up a bit larger than I first wanted, but it will have to do for now. I'm tweaking the fading to be as smooth as possible.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
